programme.title: Telemovie: Pengantin Lari
programme.desc: Mira melarikan diri semasa hari perkahwinannya kerana tidak mahu berkahwin dengan lelaki yang meminangnya. Mira telah ke rumah Nita di kuala lumpur. Mira mencari kerja namun tidak sesuai dengannya. Nita membantu Mira mendapatkan kerja di syarikat arman sebagai pembantu peribadi. Mira meletak jawatan kerana mahu pulang ke kampung untuk meminta maaf pada ibu bapanya. Ibu bapa Mira telah memberitahu siapa sebenar bakal suaminya. Mira terkejut kerana orang itu adalah Arman. Mira akhirnya menerima Arman dan mereka berkahwin. Pelakon: Chacha Maembong, Shah Iskandar, dan Sura Sojangi.

Sementara itu, zgr berurusan dengan restoran baharu dan pembukaannya. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep28
programme.desc: Selepas bertemu Serdar di Gcek, Ezgi dan zgr mula berfikir tentang apa yang perlu dilakukan apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Serdar juga akan menghadiri majlis perkahwinan Ebru. Rakan-rakan mereka cuba mencari idea dan membantu mereka untuk meneruskan perkahwinan. Sementara itu, Sevim dan Nevin bergaul dengan baik, dan dengan bimbingan Fitnat, mereka mula merancang untuk mengatasi Ezgi dan zgr. Ezgi dan zgr juga berpura-pura tidak sesuai antara satu sama lain agar tidak menyusahkan keluarga mereka. Ini membuatkan keluarga mereka sangsi dengan perkahwinan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila bersama Nizam yang bersetuju berlakon sebagai suami yang biasa. Sheila memperkenalkan Nizam kepada ibunya yang masih berada di katil hospital. Ibu Sheila terima dengan seadanya. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan terus mesra membuatkan Nizam mencemburui. Cemburu Nizam terus menebal apabila Hani mengakui dia telah mengandung kepada keluarganya, walau pun itu satu helah dia bersama Mizan. Mempercayai itu, Nizam telah menghubungi Suraya dan mengugutnya lagi. Dia meminta Suraya melakukan sesuatu asalkan kandungan Hani gugur. Bertindak dari itu, Suraya bertemu Hani dan Mizan yang baru dirawat tangannya. Mizan diminta Hani berada di dalam kereta, semasa inilah sempat Suraya menyiku perut Hani. Mizan yang keluar membantu dihentak dengan beg tangannya berisi batu. Mizan menerima rawatan pesakit luar. Ketika ibu bapa mereka melawat, Nizam turut serta tetapi hanya berpura-pura. Kesempatan itu, Nizam cuba mendekati Hani mendesak dan memujuknya. Hani tetap menolak sambil bertegas dia amat mencintai Mizan. Suraya kini bimbang dia diburu polis. Kebetulan Dato Fuad yang menyimpannya datang. Suraya terus mengadu membuatkan Dato Fuad mengaturkan orang-orangnya untuk menghalang Nizam mengugut Suraya dan memberi ribuan ringgit. Hubungan Nizam dengan Sheila masih dingin dan Nizam mengulangi dia tetap memperisterikan Hani. Setelah berfikir sebak mungkin, Mizan menghubungi ibu dan bapanya memaklumkan Hani keguguran dan tiada masalah.

programme.title: Selipar Jepun Stileto Merah S1 Ep30
programme.desc: Leto mula bekerja di hypermarket. Airis suka dengan sikap Leto dan mula membantunya menyesuaikan diri dengan keadaan di sekitar. Salah faham di antara Airis dan Stila semakin menebal apabila Stila nampak Airis membeli dan memakai kasut yang sepatutnya dibelinya semalam. Apabila Leto mengaku di depan Airis bahawa Stila merupakan kekasihnya, Airis semakin tidak berpuas hati dengan gadis itu. Datin Fairuz memberi amaran kepada Leto agar tidak berkawan dengan Stila lagi. Dia juga memberitahu Mak Tini hal yang sama. Akibatnya, mak Tini menyuarakan bantahannya apabila Stila datang ke rumah. programme.title: Perang Bibir Ep10
programme.desc: Nabila Huda dan Issey kembali bersaing. Nabila Huda, yang mengetuai kumpulan perempuan, digandingkan bersama Sherry Al-Hadad dan Ramona Zam Zam menentang kumpulan lelaki yang dipimpin oleh Issey yang digandingkan bersama Dennis Yin dan Izzue Islam. Kumpulan lelaki yang mengumpul lebih markah telah diistihar sebagai pemenang.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep36
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang melihat polis di hadapan mereka, terkejut. zgr, yang menganggap Tolga mengadu tentang Ezgi, menjadi gila. Mereka semua perlu pergi ke balai polis bersama-sama. Walaupun Ezgi, yang keterangannya diambil, dikeluarkan, mereka tidak melepaskan kerja ini dan cuba membuktikan Ezgi tidak bersalah. Terhadap semua kesukaran, perkara yang paling penting bagi zgr dan Ezgi ialah cinta mereka antara satu sama lain. Tetapi Tolga dan Serdar tidak berniat untuk membiarkan mereka bersendirian. Sementara itu, Ezgi telah menyediakan pesta bujang mengejut untuk Cansu. Cansu sangat gembira dapat berseronok dengan gadis-gadis itu. Emre juga tidak berdiam diri dan menyediakan kejutan untuk Levent. Tetapi kejutan ini tidak akan menggembirakan gadis-gadis itu.

programme.title: Mak, Adib Pulang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Adib seorang anak yatim piatu, diambil oleh sebuah keluarga dan dijadikan anak angkat. Adib merasakan dia telah mengkhianati ibunya sehingga menyebabkan dia lari balik ke rumah ibu kandungnya.

programme.desc: Oh! adalah sebuah program akustik baru. Oh! menampilkan vokalis serta artis-artis yang kini sedang popular atau baru dengan lagu single solo/kumpulan.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep27
programme.desc: Cansu dan Deniz terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa Ezgi pergi ke Gcek dengan zgr mengikut perjanjian. Walaupun Ozan menyedari dia telah menumpahkan rahsia itu pada saat-saat akhir, dia perlu menjelaskan segala-galanya dengan tekanan Deniz. Cansu dan Deniz tidak selesa. Oleh kerana mereka takut bahawa Ezgi akan jatuh cinta dengan zgr, mereka mengejar mereka dan pergi ke Gcek. Sementara itu, hari yang penuh dengan pengembaraan dan ketegangan menanti Ezgi dan zgr, yang jatuh di pulau terbiar akibat masalah yang mereka alami, dan rakan serta keluarga mereka yang tidak dapat menghubungi mereka sedang mencari mereka di merata tempat dengan panik.

programme.title: Aroma Masak S3 Ep05
programme.desc: Tak tahu nak masak apa hari ni? Bosan makan diluar? Jom memasak bersama selebriti kesayangan anda dalam Aroma Masak yang dihoskan oleh Syafie Naswip dan tetamu jemputannya, Atu Zero.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep21
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila dan Nizam melawat Hani di hospital akibat keguguran. Di perkarangan hospital, Nizam meminta Sheila masuk dahulu. Ketika inilah Nizam diugut oleh lelaki upahan Suraya. Hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang dan dingin.. Seterusnya Nizam memaksa dan ugut Suraya agar mengaku angkara ugutan diupahnya, malahan meminta Suraya akui juga anaknya itu anak luar nikah. Suraya sekadar menidakkan dan Nizam masih bekeras. Tatkala ibu, bapa, Mizan, Hani dan turut ada Nizam berbincang di mana ibu mereka berharap Hani berpantang dan terus tinggal di rumah Sheila dan Mizan pula belum pulih, Nizam amat menyokong. Sebaliknya Hani dan Mizan tidak setuju membuatkan perasaan Nizam marah, lebih-lebih lagi hubungan Hani dan Mizan semakin mesra dan saling sayang menyayangi. Dengan sedikit ruang Nizam bertemu Hani terus menagih kasih Hani. Sambil itu menyindir Hani yang sebegitu mesra dengan Mizan.. Secara berhemah Datin Umairah menangguh projek Dato Fuad dan meminta Shariff menyiasat teliti. Sementara itu Datin Umairah sedang dan akan membantu Shariff tentang hasrat Shariff terhadap Hani. Cuma Shariff diminta bersabar kerana selain Datin Umairah berharap ujian DNA dapat dibuat, dia sendiri akan menyiasat kerana diyakini Hani adik kandung Shariff. Mizan kini amat menyayangi Hani berharap Hani ke pejabatnya untuk menyemak jawatan yang dipohonnya, seterusnya dapat bekerja dibawah penyeliaan Datin Umairah.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep37
programme.desc: zgr sangat terharu kerana semua yang dia lalui kebelakangan ini dan memutuskan untuk berehat dan pergi ke hutan untuk mengosongkan fikirannya. Tetapi detik damainya di sana tidak bertahan lama, Ezgi, Ozan dan Deniz pergi mencarinya. Mereka semua mempunyai hari yang menyeronokkan bersama. zgr mengambil kekuatannya daripada Ezgi dalam setiap negatif yang dia alami. Setiap saat dia berkongsi dengannya, dia menyedari bahawa dia tidak boleh tanpanya dan melamar Ezgi. Ezgi akhirnya menjalani impiannya, mencari cinta sejati. Dia mengiyakan cadangannya untuk bahagia selamanya dengan zgr.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila bersama Nizam yang bersetuju berlakon sebagai suami yang biasa. Sheila memperkenalkan Nizam kepada ibunya yang masih berada di katil hospital. Ibu Sheila terima dengan seadanya. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan terus mesra membuatkan Nizam mencemburui. Cemburu Nizam terus menebal apabila Hani mengakui dia telah mengandung kepada keluarganya, walau pun itu satu helah dia bersama Mizan. Mempercayai itu, Nizam telah menghubungi Suraya dan mengugutnya lagi. Dia meminta Suraya melakukan sesuatu asalkan kandungan Hani gugur. Bertindak dari itu, Suraya bertemu Hani dan Mizan yang baru dirawat tangannya. Mizan diminta Hani berada di dalam kereta, semasa inilah sempat Suraya menyiku perut Hani. Mizan yang keluar membantu dihentak dengan beg tangannya berisi batu. Mizan menerima rawatan pesakit luar. Ketika ibu bapa mereka melawat, Nizam turut serta tetapi hanya berpura-pura. Kesempatan itu, Nizam cuba mendekati Hani mendesak dan memujuknya. Hani tetap menolak sambil bertegas dia amat mencintai Mizan. Suraya kini bimbang dia diburu polis. Kebetulan Dato Fuad yang menyimpannya datang. Suraya terus mengadu membuatkan Dato Fuad mengaturkan orang-orangnya untuk menghalang Nizam mengugut Suraya dan memberi ribuan ringgit. Hubungan Nizam dengan Sheila masih dingin dan Nizam mengulangi dia tetap memperisterikan Hani. Setelah berfikir sebak mungkin, Mizan menghubungi ibu dan bapanya memaklumkan Hani keguguran dan tiada masalah.

programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep22
programme.desc: Memaparkan hubungan Mizan dan Hani terus begitu mesra dan mereka juga berbincang tentang kerjaya Hani dan Mizan berharap dia dapat mengikutnya ke pejabat untuk menyemak permohonan jawatannya yang ditemuduga oleh Shariff tempuh hari. Sebaliknya hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih dingin sering tidak sehaluan. Ketika Hani ditemu bual lanjut oleh Datin Umairah, Mizan bertemu Shariff dipejabatnya, mereka berbual biasa berhubung punca kecederaan berlaku. Datin Umairah memutuskan akan memilih Hani, tetapi akan dimaklumkan kemudian. Sebaik-baik Hani beredar bersama Mizan, Shariff menemui Datin Umairah. Bagi Shariff dia sangat mengharapkan sesuatu yang posotif hasratnya terhadap Hani, sebaliknya Shariff disuruh terus menumpukan siasat projek yang bermasalah berpunca suaminya, Dato Fuad. Malahan Datin Umairah menegaskan Hani 90% adik kandungnya. Shariff kemudiannya perolehi pengesahan bahawa Suraya sering berdampingan dengan Dato Fuad. Sementara itu Suraya bersama Dato Fuad akan mengatur tindakan yang lebih agresif yang akan dihadapi NIzam kerana dia terus mengugut semula Suraya.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep38
programme.desc: zgr sangat terharu kerana semua yang dia lalui kebelakangan ini dan memutuskan untuk berehat dan pergi ke hutan untuk mengosongkan fikirannya. Tetapi detik damainya di sana tidak bertahan lama, Ezgi, Ozan dan Deniz pergi mencarinya. Mereka semua mempunyai hari yang menyeronokkan bersama. zgr mengambil kekuatannya daripada Ezgi dalam setiap negatif yang dia alami. Setiap saat dia berkongsi dengannya, dia menyedari bahawa dia tidak boleh tanpanya dan melamar Ezgi. Ezgi akhirnya menjalani impiannya, mencari cinta sejati. Dia mengiyakan cadangannya untuk bahagia selamanya dengan zgr.

Farish akhirnya berjumpa Nasha, dia memujuknya menerima kenyataan sebenar. Nasha kemudiannya menerima hakikat tersebut. Farish juga berjaya memujuk ibu dan bapanya menerima Nasha sebagai menantu mereka. Danial masih menjadi bodyguard Eliza, dia berjanji akan menjaga Eliza seperti diamanahkan. Rashid telah diberitahu oleh ibunya, dia dan Eliza sebenarnya adalah adik-beradik. Rashid kemudiannya dimanahkan untuk menguruskan syarikat Dato' Zaidi. Rahul pula sebagai bodyguard Maya berjaya mengesan Boboy yang telah menghilangkan diri. Maya berjanji akan menjadi ibu yang terbaik, dia bersama-sama dengan Mikhail dan Zulaikha akan memberipenjagaan kepada Boboy.

Mereka gagal menyelamatkan Shasa, sebaliknya Adrus dicederakan dan dirasuk oleh Zeti hingga tidak sedar diri. Dalam pada itu Gelam terus menemui Zeti dan mereka bertelingkah gara-gara Gelam tidak puas hati tindakannya. Dalam kekusutan Nia, semasa dia ke bandar tiba-tiba menemui Tok Alai. Dalam hubungan ini, tepat pada masanya di mana dengan bantuannya dia menasihati Ibrahim serta ahli keluarga yang lain tentang cara-cara berusaha untuk mengubati penyakit Adrus berlandaskan Islam. Nia yang berkelebihan dalam usahanya berfikir telah diberi petunjuk lokasi Shasa dan akhirnya bersama Ibrahim dan bantuan Tok Alai, Shasa berjaya diselamatkan dari rumah Zeti. Adrus masih tidak sedarkan diri

programme.title: Hantu Tenggek
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu yang diketuai oleh Tariq yang berpura-pura mengusir tempat berhantu telah diperas ugut oleh Tuan Sidek, seorang pemaju bangunan. programme.desc: Parti Malam Krismas di sebuah bangunan kediaman mewah menjadi malam yang mengerikan apabila kebakaran berlaku.

programme.title: Nak Dengar Cerita Hantu Ep.5 Ep5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lekaki yang membela hantu raya yang di warisi oleh ayahnya dengan terpaksa. Namun lama kelamaan dia mula suka dengan saka belaan tersebut. Setelah bertahun-tahun dan usianya yang menghampiri kematian, pak Harun mula sedar dan cuba membuang hantu raya tersebut yang mula menganggu penduduk kampung. Apatah lagi anak gadisnya putus tunang akibat dia membela hantu raya tersebut. Pak Harun akhirnya berjaya membuang hantu raya tersebut dengan bantuan seorang ustaz. Pak harun akhirnya meninggal dunia, anak dan isterinya berpindah selepas kematian pak harun

programme.title: Gamatisme
programme.desc: Seorang pelajar baru bernama Zara melanjutkan pelajaran dengan hasra tingi membuka lembaran baru dalam hidupnya selepas satu peristiwa hitam berlaku kepadanya. Namun perkara pelik mula berlaku apabila Zara memasuki universiti. Dia sering melihat kelibat seorang wanita berbaju putih dan kadang kala sedang menggendong bayi. Zara tahu ia bukan manusia. Dia mula berasa takut. Semakin hari semakin kerap kelibat itu datang kepadanya. Bagi mengelakkan dihantui kelibat terbabit, Zara mula mendekatkan diri dengan Haris, Daniel, Reen dan Jojo. Lama-kelamaan mereka turut dihantui kelibat yang sama mengganggu Zara.

programme.title: Rembat
programme.desc: Malik (Shaheizy Sam) dan Chin Chye (Aniu) yang bertembung secara tidak sengaja. Namun satu malapetaka yang berlaku membuatkan mereka mengejar masa untuk ke peringkat akhir perlawanan bola sepak yang akan berlangsung kerana Chin Chye telah berjanji dengan ah long untuk memberi rasuah kepada pasukan Malaysia agar mereka kalah dalam perlawanan di antaraHarimau MalayadanThailand.Walaupun Malik tidak mahu melibatkan diri dengan perjanjian ini kerana dia peminat setia Harimau Malaya, dia terpaksa mengikut Chin Chye kerana ingin menghalang Rosman (Arja Lee) daripada mencuri kekasihnya Azira (Zara Zya), yang memerlukan wang untuk pembedahan neneknya.Oleh kerana kesuntukan masa dan duit, Chin Chye dan Malik berjumpa dengan M.R. Baby (Zizan Razak), untuk mendapatkan pinjaman wang.Namun M.R. Baby pula naik marah apabila mendengar rancangan mereka untuk memberi rasuah kepada pasukan bola sepak Malaysia kerana M.R. Baby bertaruh untuk Malaysia agar menang.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep9
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal memikirkan cara terbaik untuk menyimpan rahsia tentang batu permata daripada Hariman tanpa menyedari Hariman telah mengetahui batu-batu permata yang dicari selama ini berada dalam simpanan mereka. Imran juga mula mengesyaki bahawa berkemungkinan Hariman adalah salah seorang perompak yang sedang mencari batu-batu permata tersebut. Sementara itu Maira berjaya memujuk ibunya yang kebetulan pulang ke kampung untuk menempah seutas loket bertatahkan sebutir batu milikinya. Dengan perasaan begitu teruja Ibu Maira bergegas pulang semula ke kampung untuk bertemu Maira setelah pemilik sebuah kedai emas bahawa batu milik Maira yang disangka tidak berharga adalah permata asli bernilai belasan ribu ringgit.

programme.desc: Episod ke 11 ini memaparkan antara lain Datin Salina dan anaknya lari meninggalkan rumah akibat gangguan dari lembaga putih. Sementara itu Zeti dengan keadaan rasukan syaitan menyeru dari rumahnya terhadap Adrus. Tatkala keluarga sedang merancang untuk rawatan Adrus, tiba-tiba Adrus hilang dari tempat baringnya. Kini dia di bawah kawalan Zeti. Dalam pada itu Tok Alai memutuskan Nia seseorang yang dapat menangkis perbuatan Gelam melalui Zeti. Bagi Datin Salina pula dia mengalami kerugian teruk perniagaan syarikatnya. Setelah mendapat nasihat dari peguamnya dia cuba memujuk Nia kembali bekerja, tetapi Nia menolaknya. Sementara itu, ketika semua ahli keluarga sedang menumpukan perhatian kepada Pak Lang tidak sedar diri kerana terkejut dan mengelak dari satu kemalangan, tiba-tiba Adrus tiba balik ke pangkuan mereka, akan tetapi tingkahlakunya berubah termasuk cara dia berkomunikasi dengan cara tidak menentu, agresif dan seolah-olah separuh waras. Berikutan itu Ibrahim bertindak mengikatnya.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep13
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rahul telah mati ditembak semasa kumpulan bodyguard di bawah Nasha membuat operasi di sebuah banglo. Operasi ini adalah untuk mendapatkan maklumat kegiatan peminjam wang di lokasi tersebut. Dalam kes yang lain, Farish sebagai bodyguard kepada pelakon Kasandara mendapat layanan baik dari pelakon tersebut. Ini adalah kerana Kasandara mulai terpikat dengan Farish. Danial sebagai bodyguard kepada Yasmin diminta pergi ke rumah Dato Bakar untuk menyiasat kehilangan Yasmin. Datin Rosnah memberitahu anaknya Hakim mempunyai masalah jiwa, dia bimbang Hakim menculik Yasmin kerana hubungannya dengan Yasmin selalu dihalang. Sementara itu, Ryan terus menjaga Haris dari gangguan Samad seorang pemberi pinjaman wang.

programme.title: London Has Fallen
programme.desc: London Has Fallen mengisahkan tentang Mike Banning saat bertugas mengawal Presiden AS yang pergi menghadiri pemakaman Perdana Menteri Inggris. Di waktu yang sama, teroris merancang untuk menyerang London sehingga Mike harus bermati-matian melindungi Presiden dan semua orang.

programme.title: Rumah Pasung
programme.desc: Ryan, Sultan dan Mayang merupakan krew program tv tersebut. Suatu hari Ryan terpaksa menghadiri pengebumian bapa kandungnya. Ibu bapa Ryan membongkar masa lalu Ryan. Ryan anak angkat. Ayah Ryan meninggalkan sebuah rumah untuknya.

programme.title: Aku No.1
programme.desc: Dua orang pengacara popular, Aznil dan Azwan tidak menyukai antara satu sama lain. Mereka juga bersaing untuk menjadi pengacara nombor satu di Malaysia. Persaingan itu juga membuatkan seorang lagi pengacara bernama Bard menjadi batu api dengan melaga-lagakan Aznil dan Azwan.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Kepala Angin
programme.desc: Konflik dua pasangan suami isteri yang bertukar peranan. Fandi merupakan seorang jurugambar yang telah jatuh cinta dengan Lydia dan mengahwininya. Lydia bekerja sebagai seorang pengawal keselamatan menyuruh Fandi untuk berhenti kerja selepas keduanya berkahwin. Ini untuk menyenangkan kerja di rumah - tetapi ternyata tidak menjadi.

programme.title: Gila-Gila Si Pikoy
programme.desc: Pikoy seorang lelaki berasal Filipina yang mempunyai perwatakan sukar untuk difahami, mengembara dari tanah airnya ke Malaysia untuk menerokai sekeliling. Perwatakkannya yang aneh itu membuatkan banyak kejadian lucu berlaku sekitarnya.

programme.title: Minah Manja
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang kehidupan masyarakat di dalam sebuah kampung.Mamak Kutty mahu memperisterikan Minah, anak perempuan kepada seorang guru silat, Ujang Singkap. Ternyata Mamak Kutty mempunyai seorang lagi isteri di India. Akan timbul satu pertelingkahan diantara kedua-dua isteri Mamak Kutty apabila mereka bertemu.

programme.title: Mat Gelap
programme.desc: Rahim, seorang kartunis merupakan pelukis untuk watak Mat Gelap. Dia juga bekerja sebagai seorang penyiasat persendirian yang sedang menjalankan siasatan terhadap satu kumpulan penjahat terdiri daripada wanita yang bernama 'Mama Bosan'. Selain itu, dia turut menyiasat satu kes kecurangan rumah tangga. Pelbagai perkara terjadi kepadanya ketika sedang menyiasat kes.

programme.title: Aku No.1
programme.desc: Dua orang pengacara popular, Aznil dan Azwan tidak menyukai antara satu sama lain. Mereka juga bersaing untuk menjadi pengacara nombor satu di Malaysia. Persaingan itu juga membuatkan seorang lagi pengacara bernama Bard menjadi batu api dengan melaga-lagakan Aznil dan Azwan.

programme.title: Keluarga Comat
programme.desc: Comat tinggal dengan bapanya yang membuka perniagaan membaiki kereta. Pada suatu hari, Borhan menghantar keretanya ke bengkel Pak Comat untuk dibaiki. Di sana Borhan bertemu Comat dan mencadangkan kepada Pak Comat supaya membawa anaknya ke Kuala Lumpur kerana Borhan berminat menjadikan Comat seorang penghibur. Di Kuala Lumpur, pelbagai perkara lucu terjadi.

programme.title: Penyu
programme.desc: Yan, Abu, Yus dan Man diupah pakcik mereka, Chal untuk menjadi pemandu pelancong. Wazir, ketua kumpulan penunggang motosikal dan anaknya, Wati ingin membantu mereka untuk mempromosikan chalet milik pakcik mereka. Cappolla inginkan chalet tersebut untuk dijadikan kelab bagi melindungi kegiatan pelacuran. Mereka cuba untuk menghalang Cappolla namun terperangkap.

programme.title: Balik Kampung
programme.desc: Ebby, Muda dan Halim adalah tiga orang pemuda yang baru datang dari kampung ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan. Di Kuala Lumpur, mereka telah tinggal dirumah rakan sekampung mereka. Pelbagai peristiwa yang mereka alami di Kuala Lumpur.

programme.title: Diva Popular
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pertembungan di antara pelakon senior, Erna Teteyye dengan pelakon baharu, Tasha. Erna ialah seorang pelakon popular yang telah lama berkecimpung dalam perniagaan pertunjukan di Malaysia, dan telah memenangi pelbagai anugerah untuk persembahannya. Pada suatu hari, teman lelakinya, Faizal diberi peluang untuk mengarahkan filem baharu terbitan Julie, namun keadaan menjadi kelam kabut apabila Julie memilih Tasha sebagai heroin filem itu. Pada malam Anugerah Artis Paling Popular Berita Harian, mereka berdua terpilih sebagai finalis untuk anugerah tersebut. Persoalannya, siapakah pemenang dalam pertarungan ini?

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep475

programme.title: Happy Enemy(M) Ep3031
programme.desc: Pei-Pei Wu and Yu-Hsuan Lee have been comparing with each other since childhood. They had a crush on each other but later became rivals because of an accident. They both wished each other would disappear from their lives; however, they are neighbors. Pei-Pei and Yu-Hsuan have been fighting, yet they inevitably fell into the destined love with each other. If fighting against each other is a way of communication and caring, then these quarrelsome lovers are getting closer and growing together. When they gradually start to let go of their competitive attitude that is full of hostility, they even start to click with each other!

programme.title: iWalker (M) Ep14
programme.desc: iWalker is a TV program which introduce food and attractive places to audience. Hosts will travel around the world to introduce the hidden gems & delicious local food in each place.

programme.title: The Lady Improper
programme.desc: Siu Man is divorced by her husband due to her fear of intimacy. After that, she wants to restart her life by taking over her fathers restaurant. Siu Man hires a new chef with unique culinary philosophy that revitalizes her. Tired of the shackles she placed on herself, Siu Man embarks on a journey of self-discovery and sexual liberation.

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Integrity
programme.desc: Anti-corruption senior officer Chen lines up a key witness, corporate accountant Jack, to testify against a tobacco trading company CEO for bribing high-level customs officer as well as smuggling contraband cigarettes. When neither Jack nor the CEO shows up on the day of the hearing, Chen must team up with his ex-wife to launch an investigation.

programme.title: Bangkok Storm
programme.desc: Underground boxer Lin Feng is hunted by the Bangkok triad when he refuses to fight in an illegal match. He escaped successfully but lost his memory. While Feng begins a new life, the triad finds him and hires a top boxer to beat him. As Feng suddenly regains his memory in the process, he vows to take down the triad.

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Meis dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child. It is only through the childs unintentional help that the couple finally manages to salvage their relationship.

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: Seobok
programme.desc: Former secret agent Ki Hun is entrusted with a secret mission to escort the first human clone, Seobok, to a safe place. Seobok, who possesses a life-preserving DNA that could save humanity, explores the outside world with Ki Hun for the first time but they are both chased and claimed as terrorists by CIA. How can Ki Hun protect Seobok from danger?

programme.title: Dream Lover
programme.desc: Ka Shing meets Kitty one day and they fall quickly in love. However, Kitty disappears shortly and when they meet years later, she is already married. To comfort himself, Ka Shing asks a mystic master to let Kitty appear in his dreams so that he can be with her constantly, even though she can only be his dream lover...

programme.title: Phua Chu Kang: The Movie
programme.desc: Phua Chu Kang: The Movie

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: Bangkok Storm
programme.desc: Underground boxer Lin Feng is hunted by the Bangkok triad when he refuses to fight in an illegal match. He escaped successfully but lost his memory. While Feng begins a new life, the triad finds him and hires a top boxer to beat him. As Feng suddenly regains his memory in the process, he vows to take down the triad.

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: My Love
programme.desc: Adapted from a Korean movie, this is the love story of school swimmer Zhou Xiao Qi and a transfer student You Yong Ci. Zhou falls in love with You at first sight in high school but You leaves suddenly one day without saying goodbye. As fate brings them back together years later, can they get the spark back in their relationship?

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Golden Chicken
programme.desc: Ah Kam, a seasoned prostitute, gets locked inside an ATM vestibule with a thief. Both discover they are ill-fated in life and Ah Kam starts telling him her life story as a prostitute, from a teenage hooker to a PR girl in an upscale club in her thirties, as well as being a strip dancer, bar girl and masseuse.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: A Writer's Odyssey
programme.desc: Based on a novel of the same name, this is the story about a father who must kill a novelist in order to find his missing daughter. Through a strange twist of fate, the fantasy world of the novel begins to impact life in the real world.

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: The New Legend of Shaolin
programme.desc: A Shaolin disciple Hong Xi Guan is tasked to escort the five young shaolin legends who have treasure maps tattooed on their backs to the base of the Anti-Qing Society. They are targeted and hunted by an assassin sent by the Qing government. Can Hong finally keep them safe and complete his mission?

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chefs delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Eternal Wave
programme.desc: Lin Xiang is a spy trying to rebuild an underground informant network in Shanghai after the Japanese Occupation. He meets a simple but righteous girl who acts as his wife in the secret mission. When Lin is captured after his identity was revealed, his wife comes to save him but can they escape from the foes?

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koos real identity?

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: This tale of a honorable fighter's retraining in the "Iron Palm" style, that became the first international martial arts movie hit and made a continent-spanning star of Lo Lieh.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rongs hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: The Comedy Of Mismatches
programme.desc: Two pairs of lovers got mismatched accidentally. The man disguises as a woman for his sisters wedding ceremony, while his lover disguises as a man to marry another woman. After the marriage mismatches are revealed, the lovers and their families are taken to court, where Prefecture Chief Qiao manages to work out a happy ending.

programme.title: Angel With The Iron Fists
programme.desc: Lo Wei directs and stars as the chief detective in this gripping thriller; playing alongside Lily Ho, who excels in the role of an undercover avenger that can fight as well as she flirts! Caught between the crime bosses known as Baldhead and Black Widow, she only has four choices: punch, kick, shoot or bombard with explosives!

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts Worlds intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: Hex
programme.desc: This supernatural mystery tells the story of a sickly wife and her maid conspiring to kill her beastly husband, leading to a string of events with spooky twists and turns.

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Shaolin Temple
programme.desc: As more people are learning martial arts from Shaolin, the Qing court orders for it to be banned and plans to destroy the temple. The Shaolin disciples decide to take their protest to the streets, using Shaolin skills to curb their hatred, but when the Qing troops start attacking Shaolin Temple, the disciples vow to protect it at all costs.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: Ambush
programme.desc: Constable Wen Chao Fan and his father are framed for a jewel robbery they did not commit. On the run from the law and becoming a wanted fugitive, Wen must recover the jewels in order to clear his family name, but unfortunately he is not the only one seeking the stolen jewels...

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: The story follows Monk Tang San Zangs journey to the West in search of the Buddhist Sutra. On the way, he encounters and takes as disciples, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing.

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: The Black Falcon
programme.desc: Jenny Hu and veteran co-star Margaret Tu Chuan join longtime0020idol Paul Chang Chung in a battle against the notorious Black Falcon crime mob in Singapore. Together they have to face forgery, fire, and even poisoned needles to stop the mob.

programme.title: Lover'S Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: Four Riders
programme.desc: Four martial arts experts live in Seoul after the Korean War in the 1950s. One of them inexplicably crosses path with a drug trafficking syndicate, and his three friends have no choice but to fight a brutal battle on his side...

programme.title: Martial Arts Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Zhi Ming, who trains at the Northern Shaolin Temple, teams up with Si Ma Yan, who trains at the Southern Shaolin Temple, to avenge both their fathers death by assassinating a corrupt magistrate, leading to a series of fierce battles!

programme.title: Swordsman And Enchantress
programme.desc: The story happens in a martial arts world where everyone tries to obtain the "Deer Sword". Lian's wife is wounded in an ambush and his rival Xiao saves her. They escape to Xiaos home and he treats her poisonous wound. This leads Lian to suspect his wifes faithfulness and results in several blood-splattering duels with Xiao.

programme.title: Human Lanterns

On the way, they meet a Butterfly Collector who is also looking for the Polka Dot but - instead of just enjoying watching the butterfly - he wants to catch it in his net and keep it in a jar. The friends see it as their mission to protect the Polka Dot and let it fly free.

programme.title: Rupert Bear Ep42
programme.desc: Rupert and the Lost Stars - Rupert pedals his car to meet Bill and Ping Pong at the tree house where they plan to spend the night. On his way he meets Raggety who is very proud of the new lantern he has made from glowing bugs he found in the forest. Rupert invites him to sleep at the tree house but Raggety announces he is a big brave elf and wants to sleep by himself. At the tree house, Bill has a surprise for Rupert. Astra the Star Girl has come to Nutwood, but sadly she has not come to play. She dropped some new stars while she was hanging them in the sky. They have fallen down to Earth and she has followed them to Nutwood. She has to get them back in the sky before nightfall or they will miss their first moonlight and fade away forever. Ping Pong magics Rupert's car into a flying car to assist their search but there are lots of shiny things in Nutwood sending them on false trails. Evening approaches and time is running out. Meanwhile, Raggety prepares for his night alone, and discovers the glowing bugs in his lantern can talk.

programme.title: Rupert Bear Ep43
programme.desc: Rupert and the Photo Finish - RUPERT lends his TRIPOD to the TWINS to keep their camera steady. The TWINS surprise RAGGETY, who accidentally aims a spell at the CAMERA, which comes alive. Now they're playing camera tag! Except if you get flashed you end up stuck in a photo! After RAGGETY, PING PONG, MING, EDWARD and BILL are all trapped, RUPERT realises that if they all get zapped they won't be able to play again or even get out of the photos. But RUPERT has a plan. The TWINS act as bait so he can outsmart the CAMERA with its own reflection. The CAMERA takes a photo of itself, which releases everyone, and RAGGETY gets everything back to normal with a final spell.

programme.title: Rupert Bear Ep44
programme.desc: Rupert Lights the Way - When the Rocky Bay lighthouse stops working Rupert and friends try to help. But what can create enough light to warn the ships away from the rocks? When he sees Ming snapping at a firefly, Rupert gets an idea....

programme.desc: What's Happened To My Little Tree? - Jess shows us his little tree: a beautiful flowering shrub in full bloom. He tells us that his little tree didn't always look like this...there was a time when the tree's leaves turned yellow! What's happening to my little tree? That's the Big Question! Jess asks Mimi for help, but she's in bed with a bad cold. She's drinking lots of fluids to help make her better. Jess gives his little tree some more water to help make it better but when he goes to check on his tree the next day the leaves have turned brown and crinkly! So he wraps a potato sack round the little tree. But the next day things are even worse the leaves are falling off.! And it's happening all over Greendale Farm! Jess asks his friends for ideas. Horace keeps cool by swimming under water, but that's no good for Jess and everyone else who can't swim. The puppies keep cool by panting, but that just makes Jess even hotter and out of breath. And Willow keeps cool by standing very still. That won't work for a dance, they can't all keep still! Mimi comes past holding a little fan which makes a lovely cool breeze. Jess realises that what they need is a giant fan that could make a cool breeze in the barn. He and Mimi make a huge fan which Horace works as part of his one-man band. Everyone has a great time dancing and keeping cool. Jess has answered the Question. Yippety Yay!

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep43
programme.desc: What's The Funny Little Creature In The Pond? - Jess is looking after Horace's underwater friends in the pond whilst Horace is away. He sees a funny creature with a round head, a long tail and a little mark on his nose. What's the funny little creature in the pond? Hey! That's the Big Question! The creature has vanished so Jess describes it to Mimi who draws a picture of it. Mimi, Joey and Jinx think it must be a fish and name him Freddie, but Jess is not so sure. Time passes and Jess doesn't see Freddie again for ages. When he does spot him he's grown two back legs! Jess decides he needs a closer look using Billie's magnifying glass. They search for Freddie all round the pond. Baa thinks he's found him, but it turns out to be a newt, with four legs and spots on its back. At that moment a small frog jumps out onto a lily pad. It has the white mark on its nose just like Freddie but this is a frog! What's happened wonders Jess. Horace comes back and explains that frogs start out as tadpoles and gradually change, growing legs and losing their tail.

programme.title: Guess With Jess Ep44
programme.desc: How Can We Keep Dry For Horace's Concert? - Horace has planned a big musical show but before it can start it begins raining and everyone runs for shelter. How can we keep dry? Asks JESS - that's the Big Question. Jess, Baa and Billie find shelter under some vine leaves. They're keeping dry but they're too far away from the pond to watch the show. Jess thinks that maybe they could wear a hat to keep dry Baa's hat is soft and lets the water in though so that's no good but it gives Jess another idea. They can use the big basket in his barn as a giant hat to keep them all dry. It's made of wood and is hard. It's bound to keep them dry. But the woven basket lets the water in too. What are they going to do? Mimi walks by with her umbrella. She's lovely and dry. They all try to crowd under it but it's not big enough. We need to build a BIG umbrella says Jess. programme.title: Olivia Ep14

She worries that Francine will be unimpressed by her family's casual table manners. But after dinner at Francine's proves not to be much fun, Olivia appreciates her own lively family dinners.

programme.title: Olivia Ep15

programme.title: Olivia Ep16

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep41
programme.desc: Why Parrot Can't Keep A Secret - You see there was a time when Parrot was the best keeper of secrets in the whole of Tinga Tinga. Infact Parrot couldn't open his beak at all! Then one day some beast dares to steal Lion's mane and Parrot sees the whole thing! But how is going to tell Lion?! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep42
programme.desc: Why Bushbaby Has Big Eyes - You see there was a time when Bushbaby didn't have big eyes. She had tiny little eyes and she was always getting lost. Strange things begin to happen and there are stories that Majitu the Great Giant has returned to Tinga Tinga. Young Bushbaby doesn't believe a word of it... and convinces the other animals that Majitu the Giant does not exist. "If you can't see him, he's not real". But then she does see the Giant and her eyes grow big as planets. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep43
programme.desc: Why Guinea Fowl Has Dots - You see there was a time when Guinea Fowl didn't have dots. She was an adventurous bird and loved to discover things. One day Tortoise challenges her to find out why the top of Mount Tinga Tinga shines. Guinea Fowl can't resist and races off, over the desert, past the ocean, up to the very top of Mount Tinga Tinga where she does indeed discover why the top of Mount Tinga Tinga shines.... SNOW! Guinea Fowl is the first ever animal to see snow! Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep44
programme.desc: Why Buffalo Has Horns - You see there was a time when Buffalo didn't have horns. He had very long shaggy hair and he lived near the Swamp. But then one day the Swamp moves and Buffalo has to find a new home! The Swamp grows and grows and soon all the horned animals who live on the Plains risk losing their home too. So Buffalo decides to save the day and push back the muddy swamp. Tales from Africa.

Wally and Wenda, arent scared by Odlulu and Fritzs attempt at creating a haunted house with goofy Halloween decorations. So Odlulu uses the magical Haunted House Key to bring a few of the decorations to life.

Tag handles it at first, but when the responsibilities start to stack up, she realizes that being Mom is much harder than she thought. \ Tag and Scooch are excited to get to know Kit, who has organized a bunch of cat-ivities for the day. But when Kit realizes she accidentally scratched up Frank and Beanss tree, she, Tag and Scooch find a way to make it up to them.

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep13
programme.desc: Postman Pat's Camping Chaos - Lauren and Sara lead a camping trip to the Scottish Highlands, but disaster strikes when Ajay and PC Selby are stuck in Pencaster with the tent and cooking equipment. Pat must transport them to the Highlands in the SDS Plane and put up the tent before nightfall in order to accomplish his mission. When a Highland cow gets into the tent and refuses to leave, Pat comes up with a plan for Alf to team up with Bill and coax the cow out with their father-and-son cow call - and Bill helps Alf move his own cow, who turns out to be missing Bill.

programme.title: Postman Pat: Special Delivery Service Ep14
programme.desc: Postman Pat And The King's Armour - It's Knights and Dragons Day at school and Pat has to travel to a Welsh castle to pick up some ancient artefacts and Sarah Gilbertson's Auntie Jackie! Pat is rather partial to a suit of armour - and when he's presented with a real one at the castle, he can't resist trying it on! But the suit gets stuck shut, leaving the excitable children wondering where their artefacts are! As they wait, Sarah Gilbertson starts telling them tales of the mysterious Stone of Penrhys and her ancestor King Gilbertson' and his knightly adventures, which Bill is loathe to believe. Unable to free himself from the suit of armour, Pat has no choice but to fly back Greendale wearing it! At the school, the children are enraptured when the plane lands and a real knight steps out! It must be King Gilbertson'! To Sarah G's delight, Auntie Jackie emerges from the plane - and Bill becomes a hero when he discovers to real purpose of the mysterious Stone of Penrhys - it opens the suit of armour!
